data.title: TaskList 1stclass
data.meta_description: TaskList_1stClass - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document contains a list of 106 game and app projects with details like the project name, title, person in charge, and file name. It includes projects developed for iOS and Android platforms across different genres like games, educational apps, camera apps and more. The projects are divided among 15 people and cover a wide range of mobile game and app types targeting both phones and tablets.
